  "text": "SModel [CITATION_1] and Tex-Sys [CITATION_2] are tools that fall into the category of tools that require programming skills. SModel is a Bayesian student modeling component, which provides services to a group of agents in the CORBA platform. Tex-Sys is another example in the same category, which provides a generic module for designing ITS components (domain model, and student model) for any given domain.",
